com.ihealth.communication.control

Class BgProfile

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ihealth.communication.control.BgProfile

  • public class BgProfile
extends java.lang.Object
    Public APIs for the Bg serials device profiles

    Clients need to calliHealthDevicesManager.registerClientCallback(com.ihealth.communication.manager.iHealthDevicesCallback) register. When new data from Bg5 device, The CallbackiHealthDevicesCallback.onDeviceNotify(java.lang.String, java.lang.String, java.lang.String, java.lang.String) can be triggered should call.
